  "prompt": "Which is the highest rated movie by IMDb (whether Hollywood or Bollywood)?",
  "response": "As of October 2023, the highest-rated movie on IMDb (Internet Movie Database) is **\"The Shawshank Redemption\"** (1994), directed by Frank Darabont. It has consistently held the top spot on IMDb's Top 250 Movies list for many years. The film is a Hollywood production and stars Tim Robbins and Morgan Freeman.\n\nIn Bollywood, the highest-rated movie on IMDb is **\"12th Fail\"** (2023), directed by Vidhu Vinod Chopra, starring Vikrant Massey and Medha Shankar, based on an inspiring true story of an IPS officer overcoming challenges to achieve his dream. Other highly-rated Bollywood films include **\"3 Idiots\"** (2009) and **\"Taare Zameen Par\"** (2007), but none have surpassed the global acclaim and ratings of Hollywood's top films like \"The Shawshank Redemption.\"\n\nFor the most up-to-date information, you can check IMDb directly.",
